The government's decision:
Swami Ramanand Tirtha Rural Government Medical College under the control of the department

Administrative sanction is being granted for the repair of the Main Administrative Building / Dean's Office Building at Hospital, Ambajogai with a budget of Rs. 9,49,68, 000 / - (Rupees Nine Crore, Ninety Five Lakh, Sixty Two Thousand only) (inclusive of all taxes) subject to the following conditions.
Conditions: - 1) The ownership of the land should be settled before this work is done.
2) If the work is under the jurisdiction of the Archaeological Department, prior permission of the concerned department as well as the Municipal Corporation and similar authorities should be taken.

3) Government Circular No. 2017 / P.R. 2017 for the purpose of processing of matters outside the State List while granting technical approval. Action should be taken as per No. 11 / Planning-3, dated 11.04.2017.

4) Suggestions issued under the Government Decision dated 24.08.2017 from the Department of Industry, Power and Labour should be considered by adopting the e-tendering system for procurement related matters in the proposal.
5) The Department of Environment, Government of India Decision No. - ENV-2013 / Q. No. 177 / T. Action should be taken as per the guidelines mentioned in No. 1, dated 10th January, 2014.
